현재 리포지토리에는 실제 소스 코드가 없고, 개발 가이드 및 스킬 문서만 있습니다. 제공된 정보를 바탕으로 팔로우 기능 관련 코드가 어떻게 구현되어야 하는지에 대한 종합 리포트를 작성하겠습니다.

## 팔로우 기능 관련 코드 분석 리포트

### 현재 상황

현재 리포지토리에는 **Maum App Backend Mono** 프로젝트의 아키텍처 가이드와 개발 스킬 문서만 포함되어 있으며, 실제 소스 코드는 없습니다. 그러나 프로젝트 문서에서 팔로우(Follow) 기능이 명시적으로 언급되어 있습니다.

### 팔로우 기능의 위치 및 구조

#### 1. Entity 및 Repository (domain 모듈)

프로젝트 가이드에 따르면, Follow 엔티티는 다음과 같이 구성되어야 합니다:

**예상 위치**: `/domain/src/main/kotlin/com/maum/backend/entity/follow/`

```kotlin
// 예상 구현 패턴 (가이드 기반)
@Entity
@Table(catalog = "maum", name = "follow")
class FollowEntity(
    @Id
    @GeneratedValue(generator = "uuid2")
    @GenericGenerator(name = "uuid2", strategy = "uuid2")
    val id: String = "",

    // 비즈니스 필드
    val followerId: String,      // 팔로우 신청자
    val followingId: String,     // 팔로우 대상자
    val status: Int = 0,         // 팔로우 상태 (0=요청, 1=승인, 2=거부 등)

    // 감사 필드
    @CreatedDate
    @Column(columnDefinition = "datetime(3)", nullable = false, updatable = false)
    var createdAt: LocalDateTime = LocalDateTime.now(),

    @LastModifiedDate
    var updatedAt: LocalDateTime = LocalDateTime.now(),
)
```

**Repository 위치**: `/domain/src/main/kotlin/com/maum/backend/repository/follow/`

```kotlin
// 예상 구현 패턴
interface FollowRepository : JpaRepository<FollowEntity, String> {
    // 팔로워 목록 조회
    fun findByFollowingId(followingId: String): List<FollowEntity>
    fun findByFollowingIdAndStatus(followingId: String, status: Int): List<FollowEntity>

    // 팔로우 중 목록 조회
    fun findByFollowerId(followerId: String): List<FollowEntity>
    fun findByFollowerIdAndStatus(followerId: String, status: Int): List<FollowEntity>

    // 중복 체크
    fun findByFollowerIdAndFollowingId(followerId: String, followingId: String): FollowEntity?

    // 삭제된 팔로우 제외 조회
    @Query("""
        SELECT f FROM FollowEntity f
        WHERE f.followingId = :followingId 
        AND f.status = 1
        ORDER BY f.createdAt DESC
    """)
    fun findActiveFollowersWithPagination(
        @Param("followingId") followingId: String,
        pageable: Pageable
    ): Page<FollowEntity>
}
```

#### 2. Catalog 정보

entity-skill 문서에 따르면:

| Catalog | 도메인 |
|---------|--------|
| `maum` | user, profile, call, product, **follow** |

따라서 Follow 엔티티는 `maum` 카탈로그를 사용합니다.

#### 3. Protocol Buffers 정의 (gRPC)

**위치**: `/protobuf/src/main/proto/follow/follow.proto`

```protobuf
syntax = "proto3";
package follow;

option java_multiple_files = true;
option java_package = "com.maum.backend.protobuf.follow";

service FollowService {
  rpc GetFollowers(GetFollowersRequest) returns (GetFollowersResponse);
  rpc GetFollowing(GetFollowingRequest) returns (GetFollowingResponse);
  rpc CreateFollow(CreateFollowRequest) returns (CreateFollowResponse);
  rpc ApproveFollow(ApproveFollowRequest) returns (ApproveFollowResponse);
  rpc RejectFollow(RejectFollowRequest) returns (RejectFollowResponse);
  rpc DeleteFollow(DeleteFollowRequest) returns (DeleteFollowResponse);
  rpc GetFollowStatus(GetFollowStatusRequest) returns (GetFollowStatusResponse);
}

message GetFollowersRequest {
  string user_id = 1;
  int32 limit = 2;
  int32 offset = 3;
}

message GetFollowersResponse {
  repeated FollowInfo followers = 1;
  int32 total_count = 2;
}

message CreateFollowRequest {
  string follower_id = 1;
  string following_id = 2;
}

message CreateFollowResponse {
  Follow follow = 1;
}

message Follow {
  string id = 1;
  string follower_id = 2;
  string following_id = 3;
  int32 status = 4;      // 0=요청, 1=승인, 2=거부
  string created_at = 5;
}
```

#### 4. Service 계층 (비즈니스 로직)

**위치**: `/user/src/main/kotlin/com/maum/backend/service/follow/` 또는 별도 follow 모듈

```kotlin
@Service
@Transactional
class FollowService(
    private val followRepository: FollowRepository,
    private val userRepository: UserRepository,
) {

    // 팔로우 신청
    fun createFollow(followerId: String, followingId: String): FollowEntity {
        // 자신에게 팔로우 불가
        if (followerId == followingId) {
            throw IllegalArgumentException("Cannot follow yourself")
        }

        // 중복 팔로우 체크
        val existing = followRepository.findByFollowerIdAndFollowingId(followerId, followingId)
        if (existing != null) {
            throw DuplicateFollowException("Already following")
        }

        // 사용자 존재 확인
        userRepository.findById(followingId)
            .orElseThrow { NotFoundException("User not found: $followingId") }

        return followRepository.save(
            FollowEntity(
                followerId = followerId,
                followingId = followingId,
                status = 0 // 요청 대기 상태
            )
        )
    }

    // 팔로우 수락
    @Transactional
    fun approveFollow(followId: String): FollowEntity {
        val follow = followRepository.findById(followId)
            .orElseThrow { NotFoundException("Follow request not found") }

        return followRepository.save(follow.copy(status = 1))
    }

    // 팔로우 거부
    @Transactional
    fun rejectFollow(followId: String) {
        val follow = followRepository.findById(followId)
            .orElseThrow { NotFoundException("Follow request not found") }

        followRepository.delete(follow)
    }

    // 팔로우 취소
    @Transactional
    fun deleteFollow(followerId: String, followingId: String) {
        val follow = followRepository.findByFollowerIdAndFollowingId(followerId, followingId)
            ?: throw NotFoundException("Follow relationship not found")

        followRepository.delete(follow)
    }

    // 팔로워 목록 조회
    @Transactional(readOnly = true)
    fun getFollowers(userId: String, pageable: Pageable): Page<FollowEntity> {
        return followRepository.findActiveFollowersWithPagination(userId, pageable)
    }

    // 팔로우 중 목록 조회
    @Transactional(readOnly = true)
    fun getFollowing(userId: String): List<FollowEntity> {
        return followRepository.findByFollowerIdAndStatus(userId, 1)
    }

    // 팔로우 상태 확인
    @Transactional(readOnly = true)
    fun getFollowStatus(followerId: String, followingId: String): Int {
        return followRepository.findByFollowerIdAndFollowingId(followerId, followingId)
            ?.status ?: -1 // -1 = 팔로우 없음
    }
}
```

#### 5. gRPC Service 구현

**위치**: `/user/src/main/kotlin/com/maum/backend/controller/follow/` (또는 user 모듈의 컨트롤러)

```kotlin
@GrpcService
class FollowGrpcService(
    private val followService: FollowService,
) : FollowServiceGrpc.FollowServiceImplBase() {

    override fun getFollowers(
        request: GetFollowersRequest,
        responseObserver: StreamObserver<GetFollowersResponse>,
    ) {
        try {
            val followers = followService.getFollowers(
                request.userId,
                PageRequest.of(request.offset / request.limit, request.limit)
            )

            val response = GetFollowersResponse.newBuilder()
                .addAllFollowers(followers.content.map { it.toProto() })
                .setTotalCount(followers.totalElements.toInt())
                .build()

            responseObserver.onNext(response)
            responseObserver.onCompleted()
        } catch (e: NotFoundException) {
            responseObserver.onError(
                Status.NOT_FOUND
                    .withDescription(e.message)
                    .asRuntimeException()
            )
        } catch (e: Exception) {
            responseObserver.onError(
                Status.INTERNAL
                    .withDescription("Internal error")
                    .asRuntimeException()
            )
        }
    }

    override fun createFollow(
        request: CreateFollowRequest,
        responseObserver: StreamObserver<CreateFollowResponse>,
    ) {
        try {
            val follow = followService.createFollow(
                request.followerId,
                request.followingId
            )

            val response = CreateFollowResponse.newBuilder()
                .setFollow(follow.toProto())
                .build()

            responseObserver.onNext(response)
            responseObserver.onCompleted()
        } catch (e: StatusRuntimeException) {
            responseObserver.onError(e)
        }
    }

    override fun deleteFollow(
        request: DeleteFollowRequest,
        responseObserver: StreamObserver<DeleteFollowResponse>,
    ) {
        try {
            followService.deleteFollow(
                request.followerId,
                request.followingId
            )

            responseObserver.onNext(DeleteFollowResponse.getDefaultInstance())
            responseObserver.onCompleted()
        } catch (e: NotFoundException) {
            responseObserver.onError(
                Status.NOT_FOUND
                    .withDescription(e.message)
                    .asRuntimeException()
            )
        }
    }
}
```

#### 6. GraphQL Schema 정의

**위치**: `/graphql/src/main/resources/graphql/follow.graphqls`

```graphql
type Follow {
    id: ID!
    follower: SimpleUser!
    following: SimpleUser!
    status: Int!
    createdAt: String!
}

type FollowStats {
    followerCount: Int!
    followingCount: Int!
}

input CreateFollowInput {
    followingId: ID!
}

extend type Query {
    followers(userId: ID!, limit: Int, offset: Int): FollowConnection!
    following(userId: ID!): [SimpleUser!]!
    followStatus(userId: ID!): FollowStats!
    isFollowing(userId: ID!, targetId: ID!): Boolean!
}

extend type Mutation {
    createFollow(input: CreateFollowInput!): Follow!
    approveFollow(followId: ID!): Follow!
    rejectFollow(followId: ID!): Boolean!
    deleteFollow(followingId: ID!): Boolean!
}

type FollowConnection {
    edges: [FollowEdge!]!
    pageInfo: PageInfo!
    totalCount: Int!
}

type FollowEdge {
    node: Follow!
    cursor: String!
}
```

#### 7. GraphQL Controller (API Gateway)

**위치**: `/graphql/src/main/kotlin/com/maum/backend/controller/follow/`

```kotlin
@Controller
class FollowController(
    private val followService: FollowService,
    private val userService: UserService,
) {

    @QueryMapping
    @PreAuthorize("hasAuthority('User')")
    fun followers(
        @UserId userId: String,
        @Argument limit: Int?,
        @Argument offset: Int?,
    ): FollowConnection {
        val response = followService.getFollowers(
            userId,
            limit ?: 20,
            offset ?: 0
        )
        return response.toConnection()
    }

    @QueryMapping
    @PreAuthorize("hasAuthority('User')")
    fun isFollowing(
        @UserId userId: String,
        @Argument targetId: String,
    ): Boolean {
        val status = followService.getFollowStatus(userId, targetId)
        return status == 1 // 1 = 승인된 팔로우
    }

    @MutationMapping
    @PreAuthorize("hasAuthority('User')")
    fun createFollow(
        @UserId followerId: String,
        @Argument input: CreateFollowInput,
    ): Follow {
        val follow = followService.createFollow(followerId, input.followingId)
        return follow.toResponse()
    }

    @MutationMapping
    @PreAuthorize("hasAuthority('User')")
    fun deleteFollow(
        @UserId followerId: String,
        @Argument followingId: String,
    ): Boolean {
        followService.deleteFollow(followerId, followingId)
        return true
    }
}
```

#### 8. GraphQL Service (gRPC Client)

**위치**: `/graphql/src/main/kotlin/com/maum/backend/service/follow/`

```kotlin
@Service
class FollowService {
    @GrpcClient("follow-grpc")
    private lateinit var followStub: FollowServiceGrpc.FollowServiceBlockingStub

    fun getFollowers(userId: String, limit: Int, offset: Int): GetFollowersResponse {
        val request = GetFollowersRequest.newBuilder()
            .setUserId(userId)
            .setLimit(limit)
            .setOffset(offset)
            .build()

        return try {
            followStub.getFollowers(request)
        } catch (e: StatusRuntimeException) {
            throw CustomGraphQLException(e.trailers!!, e.status.description)
        }
    }

    fun createFollow(followerId: String, followingId: String): CreateFollowResponse {
        val request = CreateFollowRequest.newBuilder()
            .setFollowerId(followerId)
            .setFollowingId(followingId)
            .build()

        return try {
            followStub.createFollow(request)
        } catch (e: StatusRuntimeException) {
            throw CustomGraphQLException(e.trailers!!, e.status.description)
        }
    }
}
```

#### 9. 테스트 파일

**위치**: `/user/src/test/kotlin/com/maum/backend/service/follow/FollowServiceTest.kt`

```kotlin
@ExtendWith(MockitoExtension::class)
class FollowServiceTest {

    @Mock
    private lateinit var followRepository: FollowRepository

    @Mock
    private lateinit var userRepository: UserRepository

    @InjectMocks
    private lateinit var followService: FollowService

    @Test
    fun `should create follow request successfully`() {
        // given
        val followerId = "user-1"
        val followingId = "user-2"
        val entity = FollowEntity(
            followerId = followerId,
            followingId = followingId,
            status = 0
        )

        `when`(userRepository.findById(followingId))
            .thenReturn(Optional.of(UserEntity(id = followingId)))
        `when`(followRepository.save(any())).thenReturn(entity)

        // when
        val result = followService.createFollow(followerId, followingId)

        // then
        assertThat(result.followerId).isEqualTo(followerId)
        assertThat(result.followingId).isEqualTo(followingId)
        assertThat(result.status).isEqualTo(0)
        verify(followRepository).save(any())
    }

    @Test
    fun `should throw when trying to follow self`() {
        // when & then
        assertThrows<IllegalArgumentException> {
            followService.createFollow("user-1", "user-1")
        }
    }

    @Test
    fun `should throw when target user not found`() {
        // given
        `when`(userRepository.findById("invalid"))
            .thenReturn(Optional.empty())

        // when & then
        assertThrows<NotFoundException> {
            followService.createFollow("user-1", "invalid")
        }
    }

    @Test
    fun `should delete follow relationship`() {
        // given
        val entity = FollowEntity(
            id = "follow-1",
            followerId = "user-1",
            followingId = "user-2"
        )
        `when`(followRepository.findByFollowerIdAndFollowingId("user-1", "user-2"))
            .thenReturn(entity)

        // when
        followService.deleteFollow("user-1", "user-2")

        // then
        verify(followRepository).delete(entity)
    }
}
```

**gRPC Service 테스트**: `/user/src/test/kotlin/com/maum/backend/controller/follow/FollowGrpcServiceTest.kt`

```kotlin
@ExtendWith(MockitoExtension::class)
class FollowGrpcServiceTest {

    @Mock
    private lateinit var followService: FollowService

    @InjectMocks
    private lateinit var grpcService: FollowGrpcService

    @Test
    fun `should return followers via gRPC`() {
        // given
        val request = GetFollowersRequest.newBuilder()
            .setUserId("user-1")
            .setLimit(20)
            .setOffset(0)
            .build()

        val responseObserver = mock<StreamObserver<GetFollowersResponse>>()
        val followers = listOf(
            FollowEntity(followerId = "follower-1", followingId = "user-1")
        )

        `when`(followService.getFollowers("user-1")).thenReturn(followers)

        // when
        grpcService.getFollowers(request, responseObserver)

        // then
        verify(responseObserver).onNext(any())
        verify(responseObserver).onCompleted()
        verify(responseObserver, never()).onError(any())
    }
}
```

